## [1.0.0] - 2025-11-28

### Added
- Initial full release of Sudoku Clay (sudoku-wasm).  
- Core modules implemented: puzzle generation, solver, validation, UI rendering, input handling.  
- WebAssembly build artifacts included (`index.html`, `index.js`, `index.wasm`) — deployable on GitHub Pages.  
- Basic UI using CLAY for layout and raylib for rendering and input.  
- Difficulty model based on hole-digging (clue count).  
- Basic testing harness (`test.c`) for logic validation (generator, solver, validation functions).  

